meta.expressionLhs: CASE WHEN PU_COUNT ( "EKPO" , "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."_CASE_KEY" , "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."CHANGED_FIELD_TEXT_DE" IN ( 'Change Approval for Purchase Order' , 'Change Contract' , 'Change Currency' , 'Change Deletion Flag for Purchase Order Item' , 'Change Price' , 'Change Quantity' , 'Change Storage Location' , 'Change Vendor' , 'Delete Purchase Order Item' , 'Update Order Confirmation' ) ) > 0 THEN 'With Change' ELSE 'Without Change' END AS "#{ChangesIndicator}"

axis0.name: #{ChangesIndicator}
axis0.text:
CASE 
    WHEN PU_COUNT("EKPO", "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."_CASE_KEY", "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."CHANGED_FIELD_TEXT_<%=language%>" IN (<%=ChangedFields%>)) > 0 
        THEN 'With Change' 
    ELSE 'Without Change' 
END

formula.text:
SUM(
CASE
    WHEN PU_COUNT("EKPO","_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>", "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."CHANGED_FIELD_TEXT_<%=language%>" IN (<%=ChangedFields%>)) > 0
        THEN 1.0
    ELSE 0.0
END
)

variables.name: ButtonDrilldown2
variables.value:
CASE


WHEN
    -- No Changes 
    PU_COUNT("EKPO","_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>","_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."CHANGED_FIELD" IN (<%= changed_fields %>)) = 0
AND
     -- No manual Activities
     PU_COUNT("EKPO", "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>", 
        "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" NOT IN (<%= activities_white_listed_in_automation_rate %>) AND
        "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE" NOT IN (<%= auto_user_type %>) ) = 0 
AND
     -- No Rework on Case Level  Activities
     (PU_COUNT("EKPO", "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>")
        -
     PU_COUNT_DISTINCT("EKPO", "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" ) ) = 0
    THEN
        'Perfect Activities'
        
WHEN
 
     "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" IN ( <%= purchasing %> ) 
    THEN
        'Purchasing Department'
        
WHEN
     "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" IN (<%= management %>) 
    THEN
        'Management'
        
WHEN
     "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" IN (<%= logistic %>) 
    THEN
        'Logistic Department'
        
WHEN
     "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" IN ( <%= accounting %>) 
    THEN
        'Accounting Department'
        
    ELSE
        'Other'
END
